text: @senatemajldr Cory Booker: Today unemployment insurance benefits expire for millions of Americans just as rent is due. While the House passed #COVID19 legislation months ago to avert this crisis, Senate Republicans wasted time & now adjourned . . . Where's the urgency from GOP leadership?
